# Email Watches — Example Configuration
#
# Copy this file to email-watches.md and customize.
# The gmail-poller checks these watches on each run.

## Watch: Manager Updates
- From: manager@yourcompany.com
- Subject contains: review, feedback, 1:1
- Action: create

## Watch: Vendor Renewals
- From: *@vendor.com
- Subject contains: renewal, invoice, contract
- Task: #pending-vendor
- Action: create

## Watch: Incident Alerts
- From: alerts@pagerduty.com, noreply@opsgenie.com
- Subject contains: incident, P1, critical
- Action: create

## Watch: Specific Thread
- Thread ID: 18d1a2b3c4d5e6f7
- Task: #42
- Action: update
- Added: 2026-01-15
